_sText:
This is my new hosties map hosties_assaultfun!!

this map (which still needs beta testing) has:

a gun toss court
a soccer arena
a rooftop arena
a precision jump game
a new precision jump game
many rooftops
a sewer rebel path
a one way glass wall
and anything else fun you can find

(ps: you can do shot for shot just about anywhere because of how big the map is)

the new precision jump game:
basically like gun toss with humans, you jump off the roof into one of the pools of water, the person who makes it into the farthest pool wins.


BETA2 UPDATE:

fixed:
stairs
guntoss
rebel
lighting
new soccer ball

plus others
